name: dont't close your eyes and heart
description:
Use your heart and mind in making decisions. at least you don't push someone to the abyss of someone's life, even though God has prepared the best scheme. If you have made a decision, don't show your fake plastic face in front of everyone.

We know you don't use a sound mind and a clear heart in making decisions.


we pray that you live in peace in hypocrisy.

and we still exist in a life that deserves to be human
